Pixplorer | Learn who's using images from your site

http://pixplorer.herokuapp.com/

Version: 0.0.1

WARNING: This is the very first version and may fail sometimes :)
Please enter only valid URLs
(e.g. http://www.antipope.org/charlie/blog-static/2014/11/lets-put-the-future-behind-us-1.html
or https://github.com/red-cheese).

=====

Pixplorer allows you to learn who else is using images on the specified page.

Usage:
1. Go to http://pixplorer.herokuapp.com/
2. Enter page URL
3. Wait for results

Technology stack:
Scala + Play framework
Google reverse image search + Dispatch (http://dispatch.databinder.net/Dispatch.html) queries
Bootstrap 3
Heroku